data.text:
Surname Mangam

Cognomen Mangam (Mangam ) , in all the world, is a common surname. The surname Mangam is characteristic of India, where it is quite a rare surname, United Arab Emirates, where it is a rare surname, and Philippines. Not in comparison with a country's population, it is the most numerous in India, Nigeria, and Philippines. Very seldom, Mangam is the forename as well as the last name.
